Swift Mailer:
-------------

 * See if some of the Headers can be refactored/removed
 * MimeEntity classes
   - MimePart
   - Attachment
   - EmbeddedFile
   - Image
 * Add getId() to SimpleMimeEntity
 * Add setDescription()/getDescription() to SimpleMimeEntity
 * Address the fact a base mime entity should have a 7-bit encoder
   not a quoted-printable encoder!
 * Headers/observer interface
   - Date (Date)
   - Unstructrured (Subject, Comment)
   - Parameterized (Content-Disposition, filename)
   - Identification (Content-ID, Message-ID)
   - Mailbox (From etc...)
   - Path (Return-Path)
   - Address (Reply-To)
   - List (Keywords)
 * Acceptance tests for:
   - Some Headers (which use Encoders)
 * CharacterReaderFactory (map charsets to CharacterReaders).

